---
source: tests/cli.rs
expression: help
---
Remove one comment by its canonical comment ID

Usage: remove [OPTIONS] <COMMENT_ID>

Arguments:
  <COMMENT_ID>
          Canonical comment ID shown by `activity info`

Options:
      --yes
          Skip only the final default-No confirmation

      --dry-run
          Show the exact deletion intent without removing the comment

  -h, --help
          Print help (see a summary with '-h')

Venmo authorizes removal from the comment ID alone. The CLI cannot preflight the parent activity, authorship, or comment text and cannot reconcile absence without an activity ID. The command never retries automatically. Exit code 3 means the removal outcome must be verified independently.
